### IS NOT NULL
Returns `false` if the value is `NULL`, `true` otherwise.

Note: If a field is only in some documents it will be `NULL` in the documents that did not contain it.
```esql
FROM employees
| WHERE is_rehired IS NOT NULL
| STATS COUNT(emp_no)
```
